@startuml
title FERN Use Case - Audit
left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #F7FAFC
  BorderColor #2B4C7E
  ArrowColor #425466
  FontColor #16324F
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #425466
  FontColor #16324F
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  BorderColor #C28A00
}

actor "Kiểm toán\nAuditor" as ACT_AUDITOR
actor "Quản trị hệ thống\nAdmin" as ACT_ADMIN
ACT_ADMIN --|> ACT_AUDITOR

rectangle "FERN ERP Platform\nAudit" as SYS_AUD {
  usecase "UC-AUD-01\nTra cứu audit log\nList Audit Logs" as UC_AUD_01
  usecase "UC-AUD-02\nXem chi tiết audit log\nGet Audit Log Detail" as UC_AUD_02
  usecase "UC-AUD-03\nTra cứu sự kiện bảo mật\nList Security Events" as UC_AUD_03
  usecase "UC-AUD-04\nTra cứu traces\nList Traces" as UC_AUD_04
}

ACT_AUDITOR --> UC_AUD_01
ACT_AUDITOR --> UC_AUD_02
ACT_AUDITOR --> UC_AUD_03
ACT_AUDITOR --> UC_AUD_04

note right of SYS_AUD
  derived from source code
  Primary sources:
  - AuditController.java
  - AuditReadController.java
  Supporting source:
  - docs/frontend-readiness.md
  Current frontend screen is admin-only.
